abstracts.cdata!:
The project would finance the estimated
            import component of AIDB's loans and investments for
            specific industrial and agricultural projects over a period
            of about 1-1/2 years ending December 31, 1973, and the cost
            of a study to prepare proposals for a national agricultural
            credit program.
